{"TopicId":219393,"ForumId":201,"TopicTitle":"PAIGE causes annoying \u0027pause\u0027 and \u0027unpause\u0027 notifications","CreatedByName":"Abelinoss","CreatedById":222638,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-09-09T13:31:30Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Abelinoss","CreatedById":222638,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-09-09T13:31:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.1.5(latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0windows 10 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Intel i5 4690K | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0NVIDEA GTX 1070 | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E16gb\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEvery time PAIGE talks or goes to the next talking section the game does an \u0022unpause\u0022 \u0022pause\u0022 (or pause-unpause). This also creates the \u0027Game Paused\u0027 and \u0027Game Unpaused\u0027 notifications repeatedly when you press \u0027continue\u0027 at PAIGE. This happens in all tutorials.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThere is no need for this notification, as PAIGE goes from timewarp 0x to the next talking phase where the game is also in timewarp 0x.\u003Cbr\u003E\nUltimately this means the code is being told to quickly go to 1x and then at the next PAIGE it immediately switches back to 0x. I don\u0027t know if this is necessary, but it sounds like extra lines that shouldn\u0027t be there.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#1b1e1f;color:#c9c5be;font-size:15px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022image.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022106.44\u0022 height=\u0022347\u0022 width=\u0022326\u0022 src=\u0022https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/625661934762721303/1149986795732344922/image.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nPause upon first PAIGE interruption during flight\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:rgb(27,30,31);color:rgb(201,197,190);\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022image.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022106.50\u0022 height=\u0022426\u0022 style=\u0022color:rgb(201,197,190);\u0022 width=\u0022400\u0022 src=\u0022https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/625661934762721303/1149986359889641492/image.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nunnecessary \u0027unpause\u0027 and \u0027pause\u0027 when clicking \u0027continue\u0027 to let PAIGE continue talking\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-11-09T14:05:29Z\u0022 title=\u002211/09/2023 02:05  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Nov 9\u0022\u003ENovember 9, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Abelinoss\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EBug still present in 0.1.5\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spicat","CreatedById":228085,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-09T14:20:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/222638-abelinoss/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022222638\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/222638-abelinoss/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Abelinoss\u003C/a\u003E, put your bug report out of the archive.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}